Program: Omnibus
Title: Images of Belsen - Part One
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376m74
Last Broadcast Date: 27 June 2001
***Warning: This programme describes the horrific conditions discovered when the concentration camp was liberated in 1945*** Belsen was originally intended as a place of confinement for prominent people within the Jewish community who might be used by the German foreign office in negotiations with the Allies - it was set up in 1943. Show less